name: Steelhacks
body:
### Welcome to our Steelhacks project page! 

Our team consisted of Alyssa Chang, Ata Numanbayraktaroglu, Riki Khorana, and Steven Connors.

As of 2/21/16, you can view our actual project at cmucarnival.party. However, we will most likely change the domain name for the project. If you want to view it but can't figure how to, shoot an email to stevenconnors@cmu.edu and we'll get back to you. Thanks!

Team
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
